@startuml diagrama-grafo

title Bloco 1 — núcleo do grafo (matriz e lista)

left to right direction

package grafo {
  abstract class AbstractGraph {
    + get_vertex_count() : int
    + get_edge_count() : int
    + has_edge(u, v) : bool
    + add_edge(u, v) : void
    + remove_edge(u, v) : void
    + is_successor(u, v) : bool
    + is_predecessor(u, v) : bool
    + export_to_gephi(path) : void
    + ...
  }

  class AdjacencyMatrixGraph {
    + __init__(num_vertices: int)
    + ...
  }

  class AdjacencyListGraph {
    + __init__(num_vertices: int)
    + ...
  }
}

package grafo.errors <<External>> {
  class GrafoError
  class VerticeInvalidoError
}

AbstractGraph <|-- AdjacencyMatrixGraph
AbstractGraph <|-- AdjacencyListGraph
AbstractGraph ..> GrafoError : <<raises>>

note right of AbstractGraph
  Restante da API: graus, pesos de vértice/aresta,
  ``is_divergent``, ``is_grid_convergent`` (nome do enunciado),
  ``is_incident``, conectividade, grafo vazio/completo, rótulos, etc.
end note

@enduml
